data.description: Welcome to this 3-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom, Cape Cod with high ceilings on 2nd floor, located in the East End of Plainfield. Living room has hardwood flooring and is next to the kitchen.  Eat-in kitchen includes stainless steel refrigerator and walks you out onto the backyard & patio. The yard is massive excellent for entertaining guests. Master bedroom is on the second floor and has large open closet and sitting area. Basement is roomy with washer & dyer hook ups. Washer & Dryer Included. The front side of the roof was redone, sidewalk, and gutters as well in 2022.Driveway has parking for up to 3 cars. Front Just seconds away from all major shopping centers, highways (RT22, RT78, GSP, NJTPK) Flood insurance required (AO Flood zone)
